-- Rousseff to Appoint Brazil Central Bank Chief, Finance Minister by Nov. 25
-- B y   C a r l a   S i m o e s
-- 2010-11-23T15:13:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-23/rousseff-to-appoint-brazil-central-bank-chief-finance-minister-by-nov-25.html
Brazilian President-elect Dilma
Rousseff plans to name finance and planning ministers and
nominate her central bank president by Nov. 25, said one of her
aides in Brasilia.  Rousseff plans to meet with central bank President Henrique
Meirelles later today or tomorrow in Brasilia, her spokeswoman
Helena Chagas told reporters.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Carla Simoes in Brasilia Newsroom at 
 csimoes1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Adriana Arai at 
 aarai1@bloomberg.net  